fileimporter-desc: Zaŋdi mazagaya kpɛhiri dundɔŋ shɛli ni kuli nyɛla alaha
fileimporter-help-banner-close-tooltip: Di lahi yihi yɛltɔɣili ŋɔ na yaha
tag-fileimporter-imported-description: Teebu din kpe wiki shɛli ni
fileimporter-api-badinfo: API labisi yɛl' biɛɣu bee yɛl' teerili la.
fileimporter-api-failedtogetinfo: Nasara bi nya zaŋ chaŋ mazagali labisibu yɛltɔɣili la: $1
fileimporter-api-toomanyrevisions: Teebu yi zooi yina API, ku tooi lahi kpɛhi.
fileimporter-cantimportmissingfile: Faali shɛli din barigi maa ku lahi tooi kpɛhi.
fileimporter-cantimportfilehidden: Faali ku lahi tooi kpɛhi dama faali bila shɛli din taɣiri li maa sɔɣimi.
fileimporter-cantimportfileinvalid: Faali ŋɔ (bee faali kurili din taɣiri li ŋɔ) malila neen' shɛŋa din ku tooi deegi zaŋ chaŋ di gu ka taɣi polo. $1
fileimporter-badnamespace: Sabbu din bi niŋ dede taɣibu shee m-bɔŋɔ.
fileimporter-badtoken: A kpɛbu na saha yaɣiya. Pahimi suɣulo ka labi pili kpɛhibu.
fileimporter-badimporthash: Kpɛhibu maa bi ŋmani taba. Pahimi suɣulo labi pili kpɛhibu maa.
fileimporter-filenameerror-default: Yɛlimuɣisirili din ku tooi baŋ m-be a faali maa yuli ni.
fileimporter-filenameerror-toolong: Yu' shɛli a ni bɔri ni a zaŋ niŋ maa waɣi pam.
fileimporter-filenameerror-notallowed: A bɔri ni a kpɛhi faali din yɛligi $1. Faali shɛŋa din yɛligi ŋ-ŋɔ bi saɣi ti ni di be wiki ŋɔ ni. Di ni saɣi ti shɛŋa yɛliŋ nyɛla: $2
fileimporter-filenameerror-automaticchan: Faali maa yuli maŋmaŋa taɣila "$1" n-kpe "$2"
fileimporter-filenameerror-nosourceexten: Faali maa yuli ni yi shɛli na dii bi galisi.
fileimporter-filenameerror-noplannedexte: Yu' shɛli di ni bɔ n-ti faali maa bi galisi.
fileimporter-filenameerror-protected: Faalsheli a ni bor' ni a zaŋ kpehina ŋo nyela bi ni gu sheli.
fileimporter-import-wait: Di kpebu na ni di saha biɛla.
